## Average Trip Miles, Average Total, Average Duration(Mins)

paragraphs.text:
%md
## Trip Count By Hour Of Day

msg.data: Trip Count By Hour Of Day

paragraphs.text:
%sql

select hour(TripStartTS) as hour, avg(TripSeconds)/60 as tripInMins, count(1) as count from taxi_trips group by hour(TripStartTS) order by count desc

%md
## Trip Count By Day Of Month

msg.data: Trip Count By Day Of Month

paragraphs.text:
%sql
select TripStartDay, avg(TripSeconds)/60 as tripInMins, count(1) as count from taxi_trips group by TripStartDay order by count desc

%sql
select TripStartMonth, count(1) as count from taxi_trips group by TripStartMonth order by count desc

%sql
select TripStartDT, count(1) as count from taxi_trips group by TripStartDT order by count desc limit 10

%pyspark

momVolumes = taxiTripsParquetDF.select("TripStartYear", "TripStartMonth").groupBy("TripStartYear", "TripStartMonth").count().orderBy("TripStartYear", "TripStartMonth", ascending=True)
momVolumes = momVolumes.withColumn("rowid", monotonically_increasing_id())
momVolumes.show(20, False)
momVolumes.createOrReplaceTempView("taxi_monthly_volumes")

yoyVolumes = momVolumes.groupBy("TripStartYear").sum("count").orderBy("TripStartYear", ascending=True).withColumnRenamed("sum(count)", "count")
yoyVolumes = yoyVolumes.withColumn("rowid", monotonically_increasing_id())
yoyVolumes.show()
yoyVolumes.createOrReplaceTempView("taxi_yearly_volumes")

%sql

select concat(TripStartYear, '-',TripStartMonth) as YearMonth, TripStartYear, TripStartMonth, count, prev, (count - prev) as change, ((count-prev)/count)*100 as change_percentage from (
SELECT rowid, TripStartYear, TripStartMonth, count, 
lag(count, 1) over (partition by 1 order by rowid) as prev
FROM taxi_monthly_volumes
order by rowid
) where count > 1000

%sql
select TripStartYear, count, prev, (count - prev) as change, ((count-prev)/count)*100 as change_percentage from (
SELECT rowid, TripStartYear, count, 
lag(count, 1) over (partition by 1 order by rowid) as prev
FROM taxi_yearly_volumes
order by rowid
) where count > 1000

%sql

select t_2013.TripStartMonth, count_2013, count_2014,count_2015,count_2016 from
(select TripStartMonth, count(1) as count_2013 from taxi_trips where TripStartYear=2013 group by TripStartMonth) t_2013
join
(select TripStartMonth, count(1) as count_2014 from taxi_trips where TripStartYear=2014 group by TripStartMonth) t_2014
join
(select TripStartMonth, count(1) as count_2015 from taxi_trips where TripStartYear=2015 group by TripStartMonth) t_2015
join
(select TripStartMonth, count(1) as count_2016 from taxi_trips where TripStartYear=2016 group by TripStartMonth) t_2016
on t_2013.TripStartMonth=t_2014.TripStartMonth
and t_2013.TripStartMonth=t_2015.TripStartMonth
and t_2013.TripStartMonth=t_2016.TripStartMonth

%sql

select concat(TripStartYear, '-',TripStartMonth) as YearMonth, count (1) as trip_count, sum(TripSeconds), sum(TripTotal) from taxi_trips group by TripStartYear, TripStartMonth order by TripStartYear, TripStartMonth

%sql

select concat(TripStartYear, '-',TripStartMonth) as YearMonth, sum(TripSeconds)/60, sum(TripMiles), sum(TripTotal) from taxi_trips group by TripStartYear, TripStartMonth order by TripStartYear, TripStartMonth

%md
## Count Of Pickups & Dropoff By Cummunity Area

msg.data: Count Of Pickups & Dropoff By Cummunity Area

paragraphs.text:
%sql

select Dropoff.CommunityArea, Dropoff.avg_tips as Dropoff_avg_tips, Dropoff.avg_miles as Dropoff_avg_miles,  Dropoff.avg_total as Dropoff_avg_total, Pickup.avg_tips as Pickup_avg_tips, Pickup.avg_miles as Pickup_avg_miles, Pickup.avg_total as Pickup_avg_total from
(select DropoffCommunityArea as CommunityArea, avg(Tips) as avg_tips, avg(TripMiles) avg_miles, avg(TripTotal) avg_total  from taxi_trips where DropoffCommunityArea is not null group by DropoffCommunityArea) Dropoff
join
(select PickupCommunityArea as CommunityArea, avg(Tips) as avg_tips, avg(TripMiles) avg_miles, avg(TripTotal) avg_total  from taxi_trips where PickupCommunityArea is not null group by PickupCommunityArea) Pickup
on Dropoff.CommunityArea=Pickup.CommunityArea
